Antagony flew through behind Perndabot and landed near him and looked 
around. She saw that the base was very impressive, but the life on this 
island could use some more color.

"Very nice" was her responce to Perndbot when he introduced the base, then 
she said: "How do I go about joining this 'Alliance'?"

So far this planet was fairly intersting, but she would see later on. She 
already knew that troops would be coming back from a battle soon; her little 
sense of the future told her that.
